Linter rules:
-No hardcoded strings (And get rid of all existing hardcoded strings)
-data layer shouldn't use '@Composable' annotation
-presentation should never import from data layer unless in ViewModel
-No unused imports
-No lines over 100chars
-Only one viewmodel per view
-No .dp or .sp in files that aren't style-files

http://googlesamples.github.io/android-custom-lint-rules/usage/lintxml.md.html
https://itnext.io/write-custom-android-kotlin-linting-rules-like-a-psi-chic-e081e032da2f